title: Paparazzi and Active Listening
itunes:title: Paparazzi and Active Listening
description:
PANTS with Kate Moennig and Leisha Hailey

Produced by Melisa D. Monts and Diamond MPrint Productions

Edited by Diane Kang 

 

Leisha goes hiking and has a run in with the paparazzi. Kate’s disappointed the run in wasn’t with a bear. They also discuss the importance of active listening. 

 

Follow us on Twitter @ThePantsPod

Follow us on Instagram @ThePantsPod
